    description: "Manages normalized cross-section shape tables that relate fractional depth (y/yfull) to fractional area (A/Afull) and fractional width (W/Wfull). SWMM5 uses these tables to quickly compute cross-section properties for standard and custom shapes without re-deriving geometry each timestep. Linear interpolation between table entries provides smooth transitions.",
