    equations: "f = K·(1 + ψ·Δθ/F) (Green-Ampt infiltration rate); A_w = π·D·(θ/360) (wetted area per unit length)",
    inputs: "Soil hydraulic conductivity (K), capillary suction head (ψ), soil porosity, initial moisture deficit, conduit diameter, flow depth",
    outputs: "Exfiltration rate (volume/time per unit length), cumulative exfiltration volume, wetted perimeter area",
